{"tid":1110550,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【IOS】點樣del走local file 但keep住icloud drive上面既file？","createTime":"2019-04-16T14:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T15:25:09.000Z","uid":10140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"588e117f69fca99623b0d6365b42083cef2c706c","tid":1110550,"uid":10140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T14:58:07.000Z","msg":"之前出過呢個post:<br />\n<br />\n點解d人成日話APPLE野永遠買最低GB數既版本 然後買icloud?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1045580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1045580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n個post入面有好多人話ios好醒 iphoneipad唔夠位既時候 系統就會自動幫你del走某d local file 釋放番d GB數出黎<br />\n<br />\n但我自己實測:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yo1rFxU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyo1rFxU.png&h=a9428579&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umZQnMe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FumZQnMe.png&h=18b4150b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仆街 明明夠位都唔可以由icloud drive上面down野呀 又話全自動管理既 重點係 我又唔可以手動del走d local file喎 d GB數就一直霸撚住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人知點樣del local file呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03a264f8bf5d9c9bfb773fd1aacf33712d39465","tid":1110550,"uid":167573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"Setting---&gt;General---&gt;Reset<br />\nReset All Setting<br />\nd位會全部出返晒嚟"}]}